nodes.text: Garek was a male Sullustan who worked for the Rebel Alliance during the Galactic Civil War and was present onboard Tansarii Point Station around 1 ABY.

Garek appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to the game being shut down on December 15, 2011.
